\pard\f0\fs28   ({\b a}) Subsp. {\b aquaticus}: Segments of upper cauline leaves forwardly-directed. Branches of inflorescence ascending. Capitula few, (20-)25-30 mm in diameter.{\i  Marshes,fens and wet meadows. W. & C. Europe}.
\par
